These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, marigold, iris
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person who growsiris##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching satire movies and the person who growspoppy##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Flower         | iris      | poppy | zinnia | marigold |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, mouse, snake
1. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the mexican##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Pet     | snake        | mouse  | ferret    | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, animation, thriller, sports
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, canadian, german
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the german is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching sports movies##2
2. the argentine is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
6. the canadian is between the person watching animation movies and the american##2
7. the german is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre          | drama | animation   | sports     | thriller     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | german | canadian   | american  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, frog, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
5. the fan of soul is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the owner of the frog is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Pet   | goat  | guinea-pig   | frog     | goldfish |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
City: prague, liverpool, berlin, venice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person traveling to venice is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to berlin is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| City   | prague   | venice   | berlin | liverpool |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

