.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, fanta, sprite
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, crime, time-travel, action
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person drinking fanta and the argentine##2
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the turkish is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person watching horror movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | coffee  | sprite    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Movie-Genre           | action      | time-travel       | crime   | horror      |

