.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
City: colone, prague, berlin, new-york
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the bike and the person traveling to berlin##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to new-york##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| City       | berlin   | colone | prague | new-york |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

