4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the colombian is on the left of the german##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
